description:
This is a 6 minute workout called 'Fix Your Posture ' from the channel Peter Donohoe.
The workout falls under Flexibility/Stretching.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Reboot Workout and The Zen Flow vibe.
The The Reboot Workout vibe means Deep stretch, low stress, total-body refresh. This is especially good for Recovery days, stress relief, post-travel stiffness. The The Zen Flow vibe means Grounding, intentional, breath-centered, unhurried. This is especially good for When you need balance, mindfulness, and release..
The technique difficulty is Beginner and Intermediate.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: Mobilize your neck and upper body with Peter in this quick session designed to improve your posture. ...
